<h1 id="api" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#api"><span>API</span></a></h1>
<h4 id="divider-props" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#divider-props"><span>Divider props</span></a></h4>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>名称</th>
<th>类型</th>
<th>默认值</th>
<th>说明</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>color</td>
<td><code v-pre>string</code></td>
<td><code v-pre>#e3e3e3</code></td>
<td>分割线颜色</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>direction</td>
<td><code v-pre>horizontal|vertical</code></td>
<td><code v-pre>horizontal</code></td>
<td>分割线方向</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>gradual</td>
<td><code v-pre>boolean</code></td>
<td><code v-pre>false</code></td>
<td>分割线是否渐变</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>width</td>
<td><code v-pre>number</code></td>
<td><code v-pre>1</code></td>
<td>分割线宽度,单位px</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>horizontalLength</td>
<td><code v-pre>number</code></td>
<td><code v-pre>100</code></td>
<td>水平分割线长度,单位百分比</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>horizontalLineAlign</td>
<td><code v-pre>center' | 'left' | 'right</code></td>
<td><code v-pre>center</code></td>
<td>水平分割线位置</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>verticalHeight</td>
<td><code v-pre>number|string</code></td>
<td><code v-pre>1</code></td>
<td>垂直分割线line-height高度</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>distanceToLeft</td>
<td><code v-pre>number</code></td>
<td><code v-pre>50</code></td>
<td>分割线标题距离左边的距离,仅水平方向有效</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
